<li><a href="http://propagation.hfradio.org/" class="external text" title="http://propagation.hfradio.org/" rel="nofollow">Space Weather and Radio Propagation Center</a> View live and historical data and images of <a href="/wiki/Space_weather" title="Space weather">space weather</a> and <a href="/wiki/Radio_propagation" title="Radio propagation">radio propagation</a>.</li>
